{"tid":1526492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心身邊警狗fd督灰","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:31:03.000Z","uid":160098,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3435f7ac24a1a7201a588edac957767b046bfb9","tid":1526492,"uid":160098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二手fced 警察督灰制度<br />\n佢地可以交名出去<br />\n就算無證據你做過啲咩<br />\n只要知你發過夢 甚至只係立場唔同<br />\n都可以鳩屈你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得發夢所有story一定要block曬啲做狗fd<br />\n雖然我知大家身邊多少有狗fd仲想繼續屌柒班狗<br />\n但係真係小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有班手足表示無比人抄過牌都被人上門拉左<br />\n唔知同督灰制度有無關係</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778164773b66a9cd3f9e66a2b47e3660a66b4621","tid":1526492,"uid":160098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"自推 機場見"},{"pid":"28d5814de37e5e189770b3f17e5878e6e1212046","tid":1526492,"uid":160098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"9月1 機場見"},{"pid":"7f2f23b05935dfb236aac4463cc620a57dc19fe8","tid":1526492,"uid":160098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"9月2 罷課罷工"},{"pid":"e004cfd39e5e8ad5a04594ca4b6ac1d7a4a306e9","tid":1526492,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"講多次要check多次facebook / ig friend list"},{"pid":"30386c8a4d3025ab803bb730b6814c6c276a3b16","tid":1526492,"uid":160098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"